item.title: About Me
item.description: I publish videos daily, like and subscribe to my YouTube Channel! Leave a comment to let me know what you think about the video! I upload all my videos at a high quality, feel free to notify me when a video does not meet the high quality standards! Use my invite url to register on Odysee and support me invite url, channel url. Find me on Discord, PRG#1385, while you’re at Discord, also make sure to join the Knuckle Cracker Discord server to chat about all of his games!
